description:
Much of my work can be purchased as prints over on Redbubble! To hopefully avoid too much convolution as to **where** to find stuff to buy, I included shortcut links to some of the more popular products.

* [Redbubble Prints](https://bit.ly/cyberArtShop)
* [Phone Cases](https://bit.ly/cyberCaseShop)

But dont limit yourself to just this: look around and buy whatever interests you ~ Any purchases are always greatly appreciated! :)
